lead_paragraph: When No. 25 LSU and No. 22 Texas A&M meet in the only college football game on Thanksgiving day, both teams will be looking to cap the regular-season on a positive note after disappointing and inconsistent years.

headline.print_headline: No. 22 A&M and No. 25 LSU Look to Cap Season on Good Note
